rComments: Professor Golato is a fantastic prof. She speaks clearly and articulates every word so all the students can understand and follow along. She prepares you for any German Business needed. I was able to apply to a German firm after graduation with help from her on my Lebenslauf.

Good class and helpful if you have any desire to work in Germany.  All she expects is that you go to class reguraly and do compass quizzes (two a week).  The work load is not too bad and the German was not as advanced as I thought it would be.
